name: A Vanishing Landscape
description: INTERACTIVE ARTWORK | COLOR | SOUND |  A Vanishing Landscape is an interactive artwork part of a study on vanishing landscapes. This interactive piece represents the destructive intervention of the human race above the environment intended as a cultural and ecological cavans, ereasing all the nuances in which humanity resides, grows and lives  with a simple and sudden gesture. IG: @franzrosati | www.franzrosati.com
